e platform - and when the train was coming in from a distance, the old }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3300048\charrsid7632643 smoky}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15882744\charrsid7632643 
 old train, my father used to say, all stand back. 'Cos it would draw you under. And then we had a spade and bucket in our hand. And it was a great thing for us, Southend.
