\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13765166 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15882744\charrsid7632643 Were you ever taken out shopping?
