\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13765166 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15882744\charrsid7632643 Did you ever go out with just your father or was it always as a family group?
