the pianist}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15882744\charrsid7632643  came down the aisle. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3300048\charrsid7632643 
